  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "First listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Why did the rider not get off the bus at Woodford Green?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "乘客为什么没有在伍德福德绿地站下车？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "I love traveling in the country, but I don't like losing my way.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我喜欢在乡间旅行，但不喜欢迷路。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "I went on an excursion recently, but my trip took me longer than I expected.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "最近我去远足了一次，但旅途花的时间比预计的更长。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "I'm going to Woodford Green, I said to the conductor as I got on the bus, but I don't know where it is.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我要去伍德福德绿地，”上车时我对售票员说，“但我不知道它在哪里。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "I'll tell you where to get off, answered the conductor.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我会告诉你在哪里下车，”售票员回答。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "I sat in the front of the bus to get a good view of the countryside.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我坐在公共汽车前部，以便好好欣赏乡间景色。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "After some time, the bus stopped.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "过了一段时间，公共汽车停了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "Looking round, I realized with a shock that I was the only passenger left on the bus.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我环顾四周，吃惊地发现自己是车上仅剩的一名乘客。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "You'll have to get off here, the conductor said.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“你得在这里下车，”售票员说，"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "This is as far as we go.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我们的车就到这里为止。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "Is this Woodford Green?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“这里是伍德福德绿地吗？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "I asked.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我问。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "Oh dear, said the conductor suddenly.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“哎呀，”售票员突然说，"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "I forgot to put you off.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我忘了让你下车。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "It doesn't matter, I said.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“没关系，”我说，"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "I'll get off here.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我就在这里下吧。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "We're going back now, said the conductor.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我们现在要往回开了，”售票员说。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "Well, in that case, I prefer to stay on the bus, I answered.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“既然这样，我还是留在车上吧，”我回答。"
      }
    }
  ],
